---
// Who I Am — Quietly-style full-bleed two-column layout
// Photo fills left half, content right, min-height 80vh
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="who-inner">

    <div class="who-photo">
      <img
        src="/portfolio/images/sharon.jpg"
        alt="Sharon Hadden Milone"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="who-content reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Meet Sharon</span>

      <h2 class="who-headline">
        Who I <em>Am</em>
      </h2>

      <p class="who-intro">
        Most people can be described as either a thinker or a builder, but I'm
        unusually comfortable as both. My career includes stops as a writer, a
        strategist, an educator, a thought leader. I love my non-linear path,
        and what my resume can't show you is:
      </p>

      <ul class="who-list">
        <li>My Myers-Briggs is ENFJ</li>
        <li>I was a licensed cosmetologist</li>
        <li>I'm obsessed with all things health and wellness</li>
        <li>I've been an entrepreneur since I was 7 years old</li>
        <li>I'm a champion of joy</li>
      </ul>

      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sharonmilone"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="who-link"
      >
        Connect on LinkedIn →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
section {
  background: var(--warm-white);
  padding: 0; /* who-inner handles all spacing */
}

.who-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  min-height: 80vh;
}

/* Photo — fills left column completely */
.who-photo {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.who-photo img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center top;
  display: block;
}

/* Content — right column, vertically centered */
.who-content {
  padding: 5rem 4rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
}

.who-headline {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-top: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.who-headline em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--rose-deep);
}

.who-intro {
  font-size: 0.97rem;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

/* Bullet list — dot marker via ::before */
.who-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
}

.who-list li {
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.5;
  padding-left: 1.4rem;
  position: relative;
}

.who-list li::before {
  content: "·";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--rose-deep);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.who-link {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--rose-deep);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(181, 112, 106, 0.3);
  padding-bottom: 0.18rem;
  align-self: flex-start;
  transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
}

.who-link:hover {
  color: var(--rose-mid);
  border-color: var(--rose-mid);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .who-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    min-height: unset;
  }

  .who-photo {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }

  .who-content {
    padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .who-content { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>
